latestPosts.caption:
Our stay at 👉🏻 @lagstal_living in Gangtok was truly unforgettable. 

📍Located right on MG Marg, it couldn’t be more central – cafes, shops, and local attractions were literally steps away. But what really made it special was the space itself: thoughtfully designed, aesthetically beautiful, and incredibly peaceful. 

✅Every corner had a cozy, minimal vibe that made it feel like a home away from home. After a day of exploring the city, coming back to such a serene environment made all the difference. 

If you’re looking for a stress-free, stylish stay in the heart of Gangtok, this is the place♥️
